summary: This mod adds the 4 sets of thieves guild armour to tonila in the ragged flagon - Linwei, Guild, Guildmaster and Tsun
descriptionHtml:
When your in the thieve\'s guild there was one thing i didnt understand and thats how you couldnt buy armour from there so this mod adds 4 sets of different thieves armour that are unenchanted requires Hearthfire and Dragonborn i didnt know i had them active. new version will be soon
